00:34:56.929 --> 00:35:03.109
lots of these examples and, and plainly some
of them, some of them in the book.

00:35:03.109 --> 00:35:08.950
What we do with free speech is we shift from
interdicting it in advance to responding to

00:35:08.950 --> 00:35:15.640
it when it happens, right? We're not yet used
to that for public speech and public coordination

00:35:15.640 --> 00:35:20.980
by amateurs because we haven't had a world
where that's been a big problem so far. But,

00:35:20.980 --> 00:35:24.230
you know, when I talk about free cultures
getting what they celebrate, a lot of this

00:35:24.230 --> 00:35:30.930
is really about putting the attention on the
people who are, who are doing that work. I

00:35:30.930 --> 00:35:36.220
mean, 4chan, especially, to take that example,
is certainly out for nothing if not attention.

00:35:36.220 --> 00:35:43.700
And, and the, the shifting of that, you know,
by no means easy, really comes down to, I

00:35:43.700 --> 00:35:48.420
think finding the groups that have the cultural
norms that, that use these tools. You know,

00:35:48.420 --> 00:35:52.210
again, back to the, back to the Invisible
College example, right? The, the groups that

00:35:52.210 --> 00:36:01.520
say, "We're going to use this to create, create
positive value." The, the, at the, at the

00:36:01.520 --> 00:36:07.839
end of any big transition like this, there
are good new things and goo-, bad new things.

00:36:07.839 --> 00:36:12.490
And in some cases, our inability to stop groups
from forming; something we enjoyed quite a

00:36:12.490 --> 00:36:16.849
lot in the 20th century and now don't enjoy
almost at all, is just gonna go in the bad

00:36:16.849 --> 00:36:18.339
column.

00:36:18.339 --> 00:36:22.369
And so our job becomes not stopping those
bad things from happening completely, because

00:36:22.369 --> 00:36:26.430
we can't, but rather making sure that the
good we get out of the good stuff is high

00:36:26.430 --> 00:36:30.210
enough to counterbalance it. In the same way
that freedom of speech means Nazi's get to

00:36:30.210 --> 00:36:34.319
march in Skokie, but it also gives us the
environment that we're all, you know, we're

00:36:34.319 --> 00:36:36.269
all fortunate enough to live in them.

00:36:36.269 --> 00:36:45.950
