but in a way, out of a kind of almost fatalist

00:36:45.950 --> 00:36:53.700
view that there is no future in the Internet
Revolution that doesn't include new bad effects,

00:36:53.700 --> 00:36:58.829
our ability to recognize and highlight the
good effects is the only thing that will change

00:36:58.829 --> 00:37:01.579
the balance in the favor of the value of the
revolution over the, over the long haul, right?

