00:39:15.109 --> 00:39:20.599
Overflow, a s-, you know, a really amazing
in terms of value creation around persistent

00:39:20.599 --> 00:39:24.930
pseudonyms for making sure you get good, good
action. And then you look at Wikileaks and

00:39:24.930 --> 00:39:33.049
you, and you think the design of Wikileaks
