00:51:13.329 --> 00:51:15.460
the rest of us see and see who sent the most
mail.

00:51:15.460 --> 00:51:21.819
So, what started as digital activism is rapidly
becoming crowd sourced PR. And that, that

00:51:21.819 --> 00:51:26.589
I think is one of the risks of social networking
by-by-by creating the idea that all valuable

00:51:26.589 --> 00:51:31.559
activities are low cost activities, you know?
